data.description: Stop your search and welcome this beautiful 2 story Henderson house to market! Located in desirable Whitney Ranch, your new home features 4 bed/2.5 ba, a 2 car garage, and stunning private pool! Pull up to curb appeal with large palm trees, and walk inside to a welcoming floor plan, natural lighting, and beautiful wood floors. The front living area flows into a separate dining area with bay window! Another cozy family room is right off the kitchen. Your new kitchen is perfect for all cooking and entertainment desires! Complete with eat-in breakfast bar, cabinet space, and appliances included! Walk upstairs to all 4 bedrooms, 2 full bathrooms, and new carpeting! The primary bed/bathroom are fit for a king/queen! Both sizable rooms, with a walk-in closet, bathroom closets, and double sinks! This private yard is an oasis! With a sparkling in-ground pool, mature landscaping, long patio, and plenty of sq/ft.. Get ready to be impressed! Low HOA and Trane AC! Come on by while this one lasts!
